message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>As a senior Paralegal and Legal Assistant, I am prepared to assist in the preparation, editing, and review of various legal documents. This includes drafting and reviewing legislation, briefs, pleadings, appeals, wills, contracts, and real estate closing statements. Each document will be meticulously checked for compliance with legal standards and tailored to meet the specific needs of our clients. Please let me know which specific document you need assistance with, and I will ensure it is handled professionally and efficiently.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
